  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses primary elections.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>provides that a municipality may hold a primary election if the number of candidates for a municipal office exceeds twice but does not exceed three times the number of individuals needed to fill that office;<hr><ltbullet>requires a municipality to hold a primary election if the number of candidates for a municipal office exceeds three times the number of individuals needed to fill that office;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies the circumstances under which a special district may hold a primary election; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
